object.script:
Pi = 3.14159 SPDUnit = 3.6
function onTick() MaxSpeed = property.getNumber("Max Speed (M/S)") Unit = property.getBool("Speed Unit") SPD = string.format("%.0f",math.floor(input.getNumber(1)*SPDUnit)) PinAngle = SPD/(MaxSpeed*SPDUnit)*2*Pi
if Unit == true then SPDUnit = 3.6 else SPDUnit = 2.236936 end end
function onDraw() w = screen.getWidth() h = screen.getHeight()
screen.setColor(1, 1, 1) screen.drawRectF(0, 0, 32, 32)
screen.setColor(255, 255, 255) screen.drawTextBox(0, 21, 16, 5, SPD, 1, 0)
if Unit == true then screen.drawTextBox(8, 9, 16, 5, "KPH", 0, 0) else screen.drawTextBox(8, 9, 16, 5, "MPH", 0, 0) end
screen.setColor(255, 255, 255) for Ang = Pi*3/2, Pi*3+0.01, Pi/4 do screen.drawLine(w/2+13*math.cos(Ang), h/2-13*math.sin(Ang), w/2+16*math.cos(Ang), h/2-16*math.sin(Ang)) end
for Ang = Pi*3/2, Pi*3, Pi/8 do screen.drawLine(w/2+15*math.cos(Ang), h/2-15*math.sin(Ang), w/2+16*math.cos(Ang), h/2-16*math.sin(Ang)) end
screen.setColor(255, 0, 0) screen.drawLine(w/2, h/2, w/2-16*math.cos(Pi*3/2-PinAngle*3/4), h/2-16*math.sin(Pi*3/2-PinAngle*3/4))
end

Pi = 3.14159
function onTick() MaxRPS = property.getNumber("Max RPS") RPM = math.floor(input.getNumber(1)*60) PinAngle = RPM/(MaxRPS*60)*2*Pi rpm = math.floor(input.getNumber(1)*60/10)*10
end
function onDraw() w = screen.getWidth() h = screen.getHeight()
screen.setColor(1, 1, 1) screen.drawRectF(0, 0, 32, 32)
screen.setColor(255, 255, 255) screen.drawTextBox(10, 21, 20, 5, rpm, 1, 0) screen.drawTextBox(8, 9, 16, 5, "RPM", 0, 0)
screen.setColor(255, 0, 0) for Ang = Pi/4, 0, -Pi/100 do screen.drawLine(w/2+14*math.cos(Ang), h/2-14*math.sin(Ang), w/2+16*math.cos(Ang), h/2-16*math.sin(Ang)) end
screen.setColor(255, 255, 255) for Ang = Pi*3/2, -0.01, -Pi/4 do screen.drawLine(w/2+13*math.cos(Ang), h/2-13*math.sin(Ang), w/2+16*math.cos(Ang), h/2-16*math.sin(Ang)) end
for Ang = Pi*3/2, Pi/8, -Pi/8 do screen.drawLine(w/2+15*math.cos(Ang), h/2-15*math.sin(Ang), w/2+16*math.cos(Ang), h/2-16*math.sin(Ang)) end
screen.setColor(255, 0, 0) screen.drawLine(w/2, h/2, w/2-16*math.cos(Pi*3/2+PinAngle*3/4), h/2-16*math.sin(Pi*3/2+PinAngle*3/4))
end

FuelPercent = 0 TempPercent = 0 FuelR = 0 TempR = 0 BatR = 0 GearMov = 0
function onTick() TransMode = property.getBool("Transmission Type") MaxGear = property.getNumber("Highest Gear (1 for Automatic)") MaxFuel = property.getNumber("Max Fuel (Liter)") Gear = input.getNumber(1) Battery = input.getNumber(4) Tank = input.getNumber(2) Temp = input.getNumber(3) Pin = FuelPercent*31 Pin2 = Battery*15 Pin3 = TempPercent*15
if Tank/MaxFuel >= 1 then FuelPercent = 1 else FuelPercent = Tank/MaxFuel end
if Temp/100 >= 1 then TempPercent = 1 else TempPercent = Temp/100 end
if FuelPercent < property.getNumber("Low Fuel Threshold (0-1)") then FuelR = 248 else FuelR = 0 end
if Temp > property.getNumber("High Temperature Threshold (0-100)") then TempR = 248 else TempR = 0 end
if Battery < property.getNumber("Low Battery Threshold (0-1)") then BatR = 248 else BatR = 0 end
if Gear >= MaxGear then Gear = MaxGear end
GearMov = GearMov + (Gear*12 -GearMov)/6 end
function onDraw() w = screen.getWidth() h = screen.getHeight() screen.setColor(1, 1, 1) screen.drawRectF(0, 0, 32, 32)
screen.setColor(255, 255, 255) screen.drawLine(w/2, h-4, w/2, h-1) screen.drawLine(w/4, h-3, w/4, h-1) screen.drawLine(w*3/4, h-3, w*3/4, h-1) screen.drawLine(0, h, w, h) screen.setColor(255, 255, 255) screen.drawLine(0, h-1, 32, h-1) screen.drawLine(w-1, h-5, w-1, h-1) screen.drawTextBox(1, h-11, 4, 5, "E", 0, 0) screen.drawTextBox(w-5, h-11, 4, 5, "F", 0, 0) screen.setColor(255, 0, 0) screen.drawLine(0, h-5, 0, h-1) screen.drawLine(Pin, h-6, Pin, h-1) screen.setColor(255, 255, 255)
--if TransMode == true then -- screen.drawTextBox(26-GearMov+0.2, 3, 4, 5, "D", 0, 0) --else -- for i = 1, MaxGear, 1 do -- screen.drawTextBox(14+i*12-GearMov+0.2, 3, 4, 5, string.format("%.0f", i), 0, 0) -- end --end screen.drawTextBox(38-GearMov+0.2, 3, 4, 5, "L", 0, 0) screen.drawTextBox(26-GearMov+0.2, 3, 4, 5, "D", 0, 0) screen.drawTextBox(14-GearMov+0.2, 3, 4, 5, "N", 0, 0) screen.drawTextBox(2-GearMov+0.2, 3, 4, 5, "R", 0, 0) for i = 1, 7, 1 do screen.setColor(1, 1, 1, i*32) screen.drawLine(14-i, 2, 14-i, 9) screen.drawLine(17+i, 2, 17+i, 9) end screen.setColor(1, 1, 1) screen.drawRectF(0, 2, 7, 7) screen.drawRectF(25, 2, 7, 7) screen.setColor(255, 255, 255) screen.drawLine(0, 20-Pin3, 3, 20-Pin3) screen.drawRectF(0, 20, 1, -Pin3+0.5) screen.drawLine(29, 20-Pin2, 32, 20-Pin2) screen.drawRectF(31, 20, 1, -Pin2+0.5) screen.setColor(255, 0, 0) screen.drawLine(29, 19, 32, 19) screen.drawLine(0, 5, 3, 5) screen.setColor(255, 255, 255) screen.drawLine(30, 12, 32, 12) screen.drawLine(0, 12, 2, 12) screen.setColor(10, 255, 9) screen.drawLine(29, 5, 32, 5) screen.setColor(10, 80, 255) screen.drawLine(0, 19, 3, 19) screen.setColor(7+TempR, 7, 7) screen.drawLine(6, 13, 6, 18) screen.drawLine(7, 13, 8, 13) screen.drawLine(7, 15, 8, 15) screen.drawLine(4, 17, 5, 17) screen.drawLine(8, 17, 9, 17) screen.drawLine(4, 19, 9, 19) screen.setColor(7+BatR, 7, 7) screen.drawRect(22, 15, 5, 4) screen.drawLine(23, 14, 24, 14) screen.drawLine(26, 14, 27, 14) screen.setColor(7+FuelR, 7, 7) screen.drawRect(13, 13, 2, 3) screen.drawRectF(13, 17, 3, 3) screen.drawLine(16, 13, 17, 13) screen.drawLine(17, 14, 17, 19) screen.drawLine(16, 17, 17, 17) end

object.script:
gears = {{-1,false,false,true}, {0,false,false,false}, {0.16,false,false,false}, {0.22,false,true,false}, {0.31,false,false,true}, {0.4,false,true,true}, {0.5,true,false,false}, {0.68,true,true,false}, {0.9,true,false,true}, {1.2,true,true,true}}
startup, reverse = true, false timer = 0
function onTick() rpsE = input.getNumber(1)*0.9 rpsW = input.getNumber(2) ws = input.getNumber(3)
type = property.getNumber("Transmission type") top = property.getNumber("Top gear")+2 park = property.getBool("Default mode")
upPulse = input.getBool(1) and not up up = input.getBool(1) downPulse = input.getBool(2) and not down down = input.getBool(2)
if startup then if park then gr,mode = 2,0 else gr,mode = 3,1 end startup = false end
if type == 1 then
if upPulse then mode = math.min(mode+1,2) elseif downPulse then mode = math.max(mode-1,-1) end
gb4 = false if mode == -1 then gr,gb4 = 1,true elseif mode == 0 then gr = 2 elseif mode == 2 or rpsW <= rpsE*gears[3][1] then gr = 3 elseif rpsW > rpsE*gears[top][1] then gr = top else for i = 4,top do if rpsW > rpsE*gears[i-1][1] and rpsW <= rpsE*gears[i][1] then gr = i break end end end
indicator = mode
elseif type == 2 then
if upPulse then mode = math.min(mode+1,2) elseif downPulse then mode = math.max(mode-1,0) end
if mode == 0 then gr = 2 elseif mode == 2 or rpsW <= rpsE*gears[3][1] then gr = 3 elseif rpsW > rpsE*gears[top][1] then gr = top else for i = 4,top do if rpsW > rpsE*gears[i-1][1] and rpsW <= rpsE*gears[i][1] then gr = i break end end end
if math.abs(rpsW) < 0.2 then timer = math.min(timer+1,10) if timer >= 10 and ws < -0.5 then reverse = true elseif timer >= 10 and ws > 0.5 then reverse = false end else timer = 0 end
if reverse then gr, gb4 = 1, true else gb4 = false end
indicator = mode
else
if upPulse then gr = math.min(gr+1,top) elseif downPulse then gr = math.max(gr-1,1) end gb4 = gr == 1 mode = (gr == 2 and 0) or 1 indicator = gr-2
end
brake = mode == 0 clutch = brake or (mode == 2 and rpsW > rpsE*0.2)
gb1,gb2,gb3 = gears[gr][2],gears[gr][3],gears[gr][4]
output.setNumber(1,indicator) output.setBool(1,gb1) output.setBool(2,gb2) output.setBool(3,gb3) output.setBool(4,gb4) output.setBool(5,reverse) output.setBool(6,brake) output.setBool(7,clutch) end

s = self
min = 0 max = 1
mean = 0 tick = 1 tickmax = 10 ratios = {}
for i = 1,tickmax do ratios[i] = 0 end
function clamp(x,y,z) return math.min(math.max(x,y),z) end
function pid(p,i,d) return{p=p, i=i, d=d, error=0, diff=0, integral=0, run=function(s, sp, pv, min, max, maxI) local error,diff,out error = sp-pv diff = error-s.error out = error*s.p+s.integral+diff*s.d s.error = error s.diff = diff if out > min and out < max then s.integral = clamp(s.integral + error*s.i, min, maxI) end return clamp(error*s.p+s.integral+diff*s.d, min, max) end } end
pid1 = pid(0.02,0.004,0) pid2 = pid(0.1,0.004,0) pid3 = pid(0.3,0.002,0)
function onTick()
air = input.getNumber(1) fuel = input.getNumber(2) target = input.getNumber(4) rps = input.getNumber(5)
on = input.getBool(1)
afr = property.getNumber("Modular engine Air-to-Fuel ratio") boost = property.getNumber("Reduce if RPS overshoots")*0.1 premade = property.getBool("Engine type")
if on and rps > 2 then if premade then out = pid3:run(target, rps, min, max, boost) mult = 1 else if fuel > 0 then ratios[tick] = air/fuel else ratios[tick] = 0 end
tick = tick+1 if tick > tickmax then tick = 1 end
mean = 0 for i,ratio in ipairs(ratios) do mean = mean+ratio end mean = mean/tickmax
if mean > 0 then multdiff = pid1:run(afr, mean, -0.48, 0.05, 0.05) else multdiff = 0 end
out = pid2:run(target, rps, min, max, boost)
mult = 0.52-multdiff end else out = 0 mult = 0 tick = 1 end
output.setNumber(1, out*mult) output.setNumber(2, out)
end
